2	 * PopDAM Bridge Agent — Main Entry Point
3	 *
4	 * Lifecycle:
5	 *   1. Validate config (fail-fast on missing env vars)
6	 *   2. Register with cloud API (get agent_id)
7	 *   3. Start heartbeat timer (every 30s — fallback command channel)
8	 *   4. Start Realtime watcher (instant SCAN_REQUEST delivery via Supabase Realtime)
9	 *   5. When scan requested: validate roots → scan → hash → thumbnail → upload → ingest
10	 *   6. Report progress throughout
11	 *
12	 * Per PROJECT_BIBLE: outbound HTTPS only, no inbound networking.
13	 */
